    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become a part of Kiba's inner growth as faces his fears and discovers mysteries of the forgotten gods.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Song of Seven is a narrative focused / puzzle fantasy adventure! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our (mostly) cozy adventure begins within the isolated walls of Kami village. A remote tribe that has cast itself out from the world.  Kiba, the future of the tribe, after tending to his duty's, meets Emma, a young girl from the outside. Despite his fears - he is convinced to experience the world from lush forests to hidden temples.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Director's Cut Patch</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In September 2025 - a major update will be published!</i> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller Support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rebalanced Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rebuilt Lighting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story / Narrative additions and adjustments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game guide</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433590/extras/f4eff31b94b436b82923ca39d2bf34fd.avif?t=1757343996\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory based and Interactive puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ beautiful / unique / fantasy environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enriching character development</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whimsical fantasy world </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In depth conversations with a colorful cast of characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover mysteries</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press to continue dialog</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Accessibility</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjustable Audio</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game guide inside the menus if you are stuck or just want to <br>experience the narrative</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller / Keyboard / Mouse support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note : There is one (short) timed puzzle and audio puzzle. (refer to the in game guide if you are hearing impaired.)</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Developer's Note</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was originally part 1 of a 3 part series. While this arc of the narrative is complete, it does end on a cliffhanger. If at any point this game receives enough attention, we will be open to completing the full story!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433590/extras/326aa4f174c0be39d2fd814b17b7f4ff.avif?t=1757343996\" width=1054 height=429 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433590/extras/845a0fc40a9537ad609e2bfc419fbc6c.avif?t=1757343996\" width=1268 height=468 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433590/extras/efaa6482a39216233cf797ee486d6ca9.avif?t=1757343996\" width=1088 height=480 /></span></p>",
